{"tid":2346980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃志光：推出「智方便」手機應用程式 需要生物認證","createTime":"2020-12-30T16:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T16:16:21.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b39a69614e716c4774f2e2557b62c985e5ae7b85","tid":2346980,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"政府「智方便」一站式數碼服務平台的手機應用程式，即日起可供市民下載，程式需要使用生物認證功能，副政府資訊科技總監黃志光指，是希望為用家帶來方便，強調程式不會儲存有關資料。<br />\n<br />\n副政府資訊科技總監黃志光：「這是其中一個方法，可以加強保障使用應用程式的用戶。這些生物認證基本上，用回手機提供的功能，例如指紋、面容認證，這些資料完全是儲存在智能電話內，『智方便』不會儲存這些資料到平台上。」"},{"pid":"d29e56fc147250e2bf1b0b9e6e707269bb6c3b53","tid":2346980,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=418405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418405&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0c7b3e2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418405&h=4e4b790c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=418405</a>"},{"pid":"d496161f3701a5a9b5d9b821a2f4f4d5ff482c56","tid":2346980,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"oj"},{"pid":"31c1cee7a22309b373a3a2f3800c8e2897cacca2","tid":2346980,"uid":387001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"點解成日用呢d食字名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790453e0814f3792f46c6f72536a32144e7854fd","tid":2346980,"uid":76680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31c1cee7a22309b373a3a2f3800c8e2897cacca2","tid":2346980,"uid":387001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"點解成日用呢d食字名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB